## Data
The following data is used in PI, 

```
 M = [  3 -1 ]
     [  4  2 ]
```

```
 N = [  4  3 ]
     [ -1 -1 ]
```

```
     [  1 35 ]
 P = [ -1 24 ]
     [ -3 43 ]
```

```
     [ 2   33 ]
 Q = [ 4  -42 ]
     [ 2  -48 ]
```

```
     [  2  3  3 ]
 R = [  9  2  6 ]
     [ 12 -4  7 ]
```

```
     [ -6  3 ]
 S = [ -3 -2 ]
     [ -6  6 ]
```

